    <item>
      <title>警惕市场风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-08-07/consider-yourself-warned-on-market-risks</link>
      <description><![CDATA[很高兴看到今天早上股市站稳脚跟。但随着事态的逐渐好转，事实上，我们正在目睹一记警钟。这是对美国股市的警告，因为美国股市的定价仍然基本完美，并且有望软着陆。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2024-08-07/consider-yourself-warned-on-market-risks</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Aug 2024 19:20:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
